genresAdvancedInfo.name: barnasogur
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This music genre is all about storytelling through music. It is a form of children's music that uses songs to tell stories and convey messages to young listeners. The lyrics are often simple and easy to understand, making it perfect for children of all ages. Barnasogur is a great way to introduce children to the world of music and storytelling.
